+# CI/CD Pipeline — Specification
+
+**Status:** Milestone 1 Implementation
+**Generated:** 2026-03-22
+
+## Overview
+
+This document specifies the CI/CD pipeline for Zend, providing automated test, lint, and security scanning on every push and pull request to main.
+
+## Scope
+
+- GitHub Actions workflow for Python tests
+- Linting step (ruff)
+- Security scan step (bandit)
+- No-hashing audit as a CI step
+- Branch protection for main
+
+## Pipeline Architecture
+
+### Workflow File
+
+Location: `.github/workflows/ci.yml`
+
+### Jobs
+
+| Job | Runs On | Purpose |
+|-----|---------|---------|
+| `test` | ubuntu-latest | Run pytest with coverage |
+| `lint` | ubuntu-latest | Run ruff check and format |
+| `security` | ubuntu-latest | Run bandit and no-hashing audit |
+
+### Trigger Conditions
+
+- Push to `main` branch
+- Pull requests targeting `main` branch
+
+### Python Version
+
+Python 3.12 (via `actions/setup-python@v5`)
+
+## Job Details
+
+### Test Job
+
+```yaml
+- Install: pytest, pytest-cov
+- Run: python3 -m pytest services/home-miner-daemon/ -v --tb=short
+- Coverage threshold: 80%
+```
+
+### Lint Job
+
+```yaml
+- Install: ruff
+- Check: ruff check services/home-miner-daemon/
+- Format: ruff format --check services/home-miner-daemon/
+```
+
+### Security Job
+
+```yaml
+- Install: bandit
+- Scan: bandit -r services/home-miner-daemon/ -ll
+- Audit: bash scripts/no_local_hashing_audit.sh --client apps/zend-home-gateway/index.html
+```
+
+## Pre-Existing Code Quality
+
+Before the pipeline was added, the codebase was audited and fixed:
+
+| Issue | Fix |
+|-------|-----|
+| Unused variable `pairing` in `cli.py:163` | Removed dead code |
+| Unused import `get_pairing_by_device` in `cli.py` | Auto-fixed by ruff |
+| Unrestricted `urllib.request.urlopen` (B310) | Added `# nosec B310` comment |
+| 4 files unformatted | Formatted with `ruff format` |
+
+## Dev Dependencies
+
+CI-only dependencies (not production):
+
+| Package | Purpose |
+|---------|---------|
+| pytest | Test runner |
+| pytest-cov | Coverage reporting |
+| ruff | Linting and formatting |
+| bandit | Security scanning |
+
+## Acceptance Criteria
+
+- [ ] `.github/workflows/ci.yml` is valid YAML
+- [ ] All three jobs (test, lint, security) are defined
+- [ ] Workflow triggers on push and PR to main
+- [ ] ruff check passes on all Python files
+- [ ] ruff format check passes on all Python files
+- [ ] bandit scan passes with no issues
+- [ ] no-hashing audit runs and passes
+- [ ] pytest runs with 80% coverage threshold
+
+## Files Created
+
+- `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — GitHub Actions workflow
+- `outputs/ci-cd-pipeline/spec.md` — This specification
+- `outputs/ci-cd-pipeline/review.md` — Implementation review
+
+## Out of Scope
+
+- Docker/containerized builds
+- Matrix builds for multiple Python versions
+- Deployment automation
+- GitHub branch protection (requires GitHub UI/gh cli — manual step)
